### ==================== PORTFOLIO USERS ====================

### Get All Portfolio Users (Public)
GET {{SkillSnap.Api_HostAddress}}/api/portfoliousers
Accept: application/json

### Get Portfolio User by ID (Public)
GET {{SkillSnap.Api_HostAddress}}/api/portfoliousers/1
Accept: application/json

### Create Portfolio User (Requires Auth)
POST {{SkillSnap.Api_HostAddress}}/api/portfoliousers
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "bio": "Full-stack developer with 5 years of experience in .NET and React",
  "profileImageUrl": "https://via.placeholder.com/200"
}

### Update Portfolio User (Requires Auth)
PUT {{SkillSnap.Api_HostAddress}}/api/portfoliousers/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "id": 1,
  "name": "John Doe Updated",
  "bio": "Senior Full-stack developer with 5+ years of experience",
  "profileImageUrl": "https://via.placeholder.com/200"
}

### Delete Portfolio User (Requires Admin)
DELETE {{SkillSnap.Api_HostAddress}}/api/portfoliousers/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

